OL,3,CLord Cameron vows to review case of
OL,4,CBriton detained in India
OL,6,FThe brother of a British man who has
OL,7,Fbeen held in an Indian prison for more
OL,8,Fthan six years has told the foreign
OL,9,Fsecretary "his life is in your hands"
OL,10,Fas the government promised to review
OL,11,Fthe case.
OL,13,FOn his first visit to Scotland since
OL,14,Fbecoming foreign secretary, Lord David
OL,15,FCameron met the family of Jagtar Singh
OL,16,FJohal, who have been campaigning for
OL,17,Fyears for his release.
