OL,3,CLord Cameron vows to review case of
OL,4,CBriton detained in India
OL,6,FThe British citizen, from Dumbarton,
OL,7,FScotland, faces the death penalty as a
OL,8,Fresult of his campaigning for Sikh
OL,9,Frights.
OL,11,FMr Johal was in Punjab in northern
OL,12,FIndia for his wedding in 2017 when his
OL,13,Ffamily said he was arrested and
OL,14,Fbundled into an unmarked car.
OL,16,FHe is said to have been interrogated
OL,17,Fand tortured, including "using
OL,18,Felectric shocks, forcing his limbs
OL,19,Finto painful positions and depriving
OL,20,Fhim of sleep", a UN report in 2022
OL,21,Ffound.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/12
