OL,4,CBriton detained in India
OL,6,FThe United Nations has and said his
OL,7,Fdetention is "arbitrary" and that it
OL,8,F"lacks legal basis".
OL,10,FWhen Lord Cameron returned to politics
OL,11,Flast November, after being appointed
OL,12,Fforeign secretary, Mr Johal's family
OL,13,Fsaid they were hopeful he could make a
OL,14,Fdifference.
OL,16,FHis brother, Gurpreet Singh Johal,
OL,17,Fsaid at the time: "We're hopeful that
OL,18,Fthe sixth foreign secretary after six
OL,19,Fyears might do something that the
OL,20,Fother foreign secretaries have failed
OL,21,Fto do."
