OL,3,CLord Cameron vows to review case of
OL,4,CBriton detained in India
OL,6,FAfter a "very important meeting" with
OL,7,Fthe family on Monday, Lord Cameron
OL,8,Fstressed he was taking the case
OL,9,F"incredibly seriously".
OL,11,FFollowing the meeting, brother
OL,12,FGurpreet told Sky News: "I have
OL,13,Freiterated to him that my brother's
OL,14,Flife's in your hands, and if he
OL,15,Fdoesn't do anything then my brother
OL,16,Fcould be in there a long time.
OL,18,F"Jagtar is also facing the death
OL,19,Fpenalty, which will be on the foreign
OL,20,Fsecretary, so I have put it on him so
OL,21,Fhe understands the urgency."
