OL,6,FLord Cameron said he would review the
OL,7,Faction taken so far to "make sure we
OL,8,Fare doing the right thing", but
OL,9,Fstopped short of calling for Mr Johal
OL,10,Fto be released.
OL,12,FSpeaking as he visited the Foreign,
OL,13,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,14,Fbuilding in East Kilbride, South
OL,15,FLanarkshire, Lord Cameron said: "As
OL,16,Fforeign secretary I have looked at the
OL,17,Fcase, examined all the paperwork.
