OL,6,F"I wanted to meet there with the
OL,7,Ffamily and hear from them what they
OL,8,Fthink. And I want to really stress, as
OL,9,Fan incoming foreign secretary, you
OL,10,Fdon't just accept what the government
OL,11,Fhas said up to now, you really look at
OL,12,Fit, really ask the questions.
OL,14,F"And meeting with the family today is
OL,15,Fgoing to help me to go back and ask
OL,16,Fthose questions all over again to make
OL,17,Fsure we're doing the right thing for
OL,18,Fthis British citizen."
