OL,6,F"I am going to take into account what
OL,7,Fthey have said and see whether there
OL,8,Fis a different approach we should be
OL,9,Ftaking.
OL,11,F"I've made absolutely no promises that
OL,12,Fit will be different, but what I have
OL,13,Fsaid is I take these cases very
OL,14,Fseriously.
OL,16,F"I am going to re-examine everything
OL,17,Fand make sure we are doing the right
OL,18,Fthing.
