OL,6,F"That's what you should always do,
OL,7,Fwhether it is someone who has been
OL,8,Ftaken hostage, whether it is someone
OL,9,Fwho is in prison."
OL,11,FDabinderjit Singh, principal adviser
OL,12,Fat the Sikh Federation (UK), however,
OL,13,Fclaimed that UK foreign secretaries
OL,14,Fhad so far "failed" to take the "tough
OL,15,Faction" needed in this case, adding
OL,16,Fthat the "jury is out" on whether Lord
OL,17,FCameron will have an impact.
