OL,6,FCommenting after the meeting, Mr Singh
OL,7,Fsaid: "Jagtar's family not only
OL,8,Fdeserve answers from David Cameron to
OL,9,Fjustify the UK Government approach to
OL,10,Fa British national being tortured and
OL,11,Farbitrarily detained for over six
OL,12,Fyears in an Indian jail, they also
OL,13,Fneed a new strategy to secure his
OL,14,Fspeedy release and return to Scotland
OL,15,Fto be with his family.
