OL,6,F"Jagtar's MP, Martin Docherty-Hughes
OL,7,Fhas been doing a fantastic job to
OL,8,Fraise his case at every opportunity,
OL,9,Fbut the UK Government has failed for
OL,10,Fover six years to take the tough
OL,11,Faction the foreign minister promised
OL,12,Fin the UK Parliament within weeks of
OL,13,Fhis abduction and torture.
OL,15,F"The British Sikh community and the
OL,16,Fwider British public expect better
OL,17,Ffrom the UK Government to protect
OL,18,FBritish nationals.
